{"label": "droite", "transcript": [{"text": "Merci Madame la Pr\u00e9sidente.", "start": 0.3, "duration": 1.2}, {"text": "Monsieur le Commissaire,", "start": 1.5, "duration": 1.1}, {"text": "Ce sujet des aides", "start": 2.6, "duration": 1.066}, {"text": "d'Etat peut para\u00eetre technique,", "start": 3.666, "duration": 1.1}, {"text": "mais je voudrais", "start": 4.766, "duration": 0.367}, {"text": "simplement vous raconter", "start": 5.133, "duration": 0.9}, {"text": "une petite histoire.", "start": 6.033, "duration": 1.367}, {"text": "Lorsque j'ai \u00e9t\u00e9 voir", "start": 7.4, "duration": 0.766}, {"text": "les p\u00eacheurs de Mayotte,", "start": 8.166, "duration": 1.067}, {"text": "qui sortent en mer", "start": 9.233, "duration": 0.833}, {"text": "sur des pirogues hors d'\u00e2ge,", "start": 10.066, "duration": 1.834}, {"text": "ils m'ont dit qu'ils n'avaient pas re\u00e7u", "start": 11.9, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "un seul centime", "start": 13.9, "duration": 1.0}, {"text": "des financements", "start": 14.9, "duration": 0.666}, {"text": "qui leur ont \u00e9t\u00e9 promis,", "start": 15.566, "duration": 0.967}, {"text": "depuis des ann\u00e9es maintenant,", "start": 16.533, "duration": 1.467}, {"text": "pour renouveler leur flotte.", "start": 18.0, "duration": 1.0}, {"text": "Toutes les grandes puissances mondiales", "start": 19.0, "duration": 1.766}, {"text": "aident leurs p\u00eacheurs \u00e0 financer", "start": 20.766, "duration": 2.034}, {"text": "le renouvellement de la flotte,", "start": 22.8, "duration": 1.133}, {"text": "et pour nous,", "start": 23.933, "duration": 0.7}, {"text": "ce sont des enjeux strat\u00e9giques", "start": 24.633, "duration": 2.1}, {"text": "majeurs, que ceux qui consistent", "start": 26.733, "duration": 1.467}, {"text": "\u00e0 alimenter", "start": 28.2, "duration": 1.0}, {"text": "nos r\u00e9gions ultrap\u00e9riph\u00e9riques,", "start": 29.2, "duration": 1.133}, {"text": "nos pays europ\u00e9ens,", "start": 30.333, "duration": 0.767}, {"text": "mais aussi \u00e0 assurer", "start": 31.1, "duration": 1.0}, {"text": "une pr\u00e9sence \u00e0 la mer", "start": 32.1, "duration": 0.966}, {"text": "dans ces r\u00e9gions du monde", "start": 33.066, "duration": 1.4}, {"text": "o\u00f9 l'Europe", "start": 34.466, "duration": 0.5}, {"text": "a la chance de pouvoir compter sur eux.", "start": 34.966, "duration": 2.334}, {"text": "Eh bien, nous n'avons pas d\u00e9bloqu\u00e9 1\u00a0\u20ac.", "start": 37.3, "duration": 1.966}, {"text": "Pourquoi ?", "start": 39.266, "duration": 0.8}, {"text": "Parce que m\u00eame si notre Parlement", "start": 40.066, "duration": 1.934}, {"text": "a vot\u00e9 en faveur de ces aides d'Etat,", "start": 42.0, "duration": 1.766}, {"text": "et m\u00eame s'il a vot\u00e9", "start": 43.766, "duration": 1.134}, {"text": "en faveur de fonds europ\u00e9ens", "start": 44.9, "duration": 1.233}, {"text": "pour le renouvellement de la flotte,", "start": 46.133, "duration": 1.933}, {"text": "m\u00eame si la Commission europ\u00e9enne", "start": 48.066, "duration": 1.367}, {"text": "s'y est engag\u00e9e,", "start": 49.433, "duration": 1.133}, {"text": "aujourd'hui, le sujet est bloqu\u00e9 :", "start": 50.566, "duration": 1.767}, {"text": "la Commission", "start": 52.333, "duration": 0.9}, {"text": "refuse d'engager", "start": 53.233, "duration": 1.367}, {"text": "les financements n\u00e9cessaires.", "start": 54.6, "duration": 1.0}, {"text": "Et pourtant,", "start": 55.6, "duration": 1.466}, {"text": "simultan\u00e9ment, ces p\u00eacheurs de Mayotte,", "start": 57.066, "duration": 2.934}, {"text": "mais aussi ceux de Guyane,", "start": 60.0, "duration": 1.566}, {"text": "ceux de", "start": 61.566, "duration": 0.3}, {"text": "La R\u00e9union,", "start": 61.866, "duration": 0.9}, {"text": "voient arriver des bateaux", "start": 62.766, "duration": 1.334}, {"text": "neufs, flambant", "start": 64.1, "duration": 0.966}, {"text": "neufs, financ\u00e9s", "start": 65.066, "duration": 1.167}, {"text": "par des fonds europ\u00e9ens,", "start": 66.233, "duration": 1.1}, {"text": "au titre de l'aide", "start": 67.333, "duration": 1.0}, {"text": "au d\u00e9veloppement :", "start": 68.333, "duration": 0.467}, {"text": "des bateaux du Surinam pour la Guyane,", "start": 68.8, "duration": 2.5}, {"text": "des bateaux", "start": 71.3, "duration": 1.066}, {"text": "de l'\u00eele Maurice", "start": 72.5, "duration": 1.233}, {"text": "pour Mayotte et La R\u00e9union.", "start": 73.733, "duration": 1.933}, {"text": "Nous voyons que l'Europe finance", "start": 75.666, "duration": 1.967}, {"text": "avec des fonds europ\u00e9ens", "start": 77.633, "duration": 1.5}, {"text": "des bateaux", "start": 79.133, "duration": 0.867}, {"text": "cr\u00e9\u00e9s", "start": 80.0, "duration": 0.733}, {"text": "dans des pays tiers,", "start": 80.733, "duration": 1.167}, {"text": "quand elle refuse", "start": 81.9, "duration": 0.9}, {"text": "\u00e0 nos propres \u00c9tats", "start": 82.8, "duration": 1.033}, {"text": "de soutenir nos p\u00eacheurs,", "start": 83.833, "duration": 1.5}, {"text": "dans nos propres pays.", "start": 85.333, "duration": 0.8}, {"text": "Comment ce sujet", "start": 86.133, "duration": 1.133}, {"text": "ne pourrait-il pas", "start": 87.266, "duration": 1.034}, {"text": "r\u00e9volter les p\u00eacheurs de nos r\u00e9gions", "start": 88.3, "duration": 2.9}, {"text": "ultrap\u00e9riph\u00e9riques,", "start": 91.2, "duration": 0.9}, {"text": "les p\u00eacheurs de nos Outre-Mer ?", "start": 92.1, "duration": 1.5}, {"text": "Il est urgent,", "start": 93.6, "duration": 1.266}, {"text": "enfin, que ce sujet soit d\u00e9bloqu\u00e9,", "start": 94.866, "duration": 1.734}, {"text": "et que nous cessions", "start": 96.6, "duration": 0.666}, {"text": "les man\u0153uvres dilatoires", "start": 97.266, "duration": 1.1}, {"text": "qui consistent \u00e0 refuser sans cesse", "start": 98.366, "duration": 2.134}, {"text": "que ce soutien, pourtant vot\u00e9", "start": 100.5, "duration": 2.033}, {"text": "par notre Parlement,", "start": 102.533, "duration": 1.0}, {"text": "devienne une r\u00e9alit\u00e9.", "start": 103.533, "duration": 1.367}, {"text": "Merci beaucoup.", "start": 104.9, "duration": 1.933}]}